<br>
Making No Drop items droppable would be bad in my opinion, due to the lack of item decay.  High end items would pile up at the lower end of the level spectrum, and zones that are moderately challenging now would become trivial.<br>
<br>
The only way No Drop items should be made droppable is if Item decay is implemented at the same time. <p><div align="center"><font size="2">Aragir Lancot<BR>
